a highspeed train plowed into the back of 
a slowmoving train in thick fog on the outskirts of warsaw on 
monday killing 16 people and injuring more than 50 officials said 
the force of the collision lifted the last car of the slower 
train off the track the engine of the speeding train ripped 
through the car as it passed underneath 
