both iraq and the united states for provocative actions in the 
mideast and threatened to withdraw libya from the united nations 
the libyan leader also urged the un security council to pass a 
resolution calling for military measures against iraq which 
invaded kuwait on aug 2 the united nations has backed the use of 
economic sanctions in its effort to get iraq to withdraw occupation 
forces from kuwait 
at a news conference in the babaziziya barracks outside the 
capital of tripoli gadhafi said he opposed iraqs holding of 
foreigners including americans and british citizens as hostages 
we are against the use of hostages as bargaining chips this is 
our fixed priciple 
