was conducted in a tentlike structure lined with bright green red 
and white canvas the libyan leader was surrounded by reporters 
shouting questions at him 
when at one point the translator said the united states 
instead of the un gadhafi said hes right now there is 
no difference between the united states and the united nations 
he also said the un security council has so far taken steps 
within the un charter recommending the international community 
impose economic sanctions on iraq but the united states has 
ignored this resolution 
the united states which has decided to stop vessels suspected 
of carrying goods to iraq has stationed warships in and around the 
persian gulf and in the red sea 
