sacrifice their profits to cover the increases 
more than 120 newspapers and other soviet news organizations 
have applied under the new press law which was approved 
unanimously by the supreme soviet in june after months of debate 
and took effect aug 1 
to establish a publication or news organization soviets need 
only provide their name address frequency of publication 
circulation figures and source of financing 
