rating and a 60 percent share of the audience last week compared 
with a 281 rating and 53 share for prime time programs nielsen 
audience estimates showed 
abcs frontrunning world news tonight averaged a 106 
rating the cbs evening news whose anchor dan rather has 
been in the middle east since iraqs aug 2 in invasion of kuwait 
averaged a 93 nbc nightly news ran third with an 89 average 
each ratings point represents 921000 homes the audience share 
is the estimated percentage of homes tuned to a given program in 
its time period 
