the following is a transcript of the final 
session at camp rerun a minimumsecurity installation where tv 
critics are sent each summer for refresher courses on how to do 
their thing 
all right people listen up this is our final chance to review 
lessons learned what to do with old videocassettes and how to 
cover the people covering a story like anchormen questions 
q whats twin peaks about 
a a surreal postmodern seriocomic drama about the somber belly 
of american life part of david lynchs brooding complex oeuvre 
it is at once darkly comic and brilliantly bleak 
q that makes no sense 
a i know but if you write that way often enough theyll 
promote you to movie critic 
q who killed laura palmer 
a you sir are a geek 
q what is the middle east 
a a large dusty oilrich kingdom ruled on a rotating basis by 
three kings the kings are ted koppel dan rather and tom brokaw 
although we see in people magazine that king dan is mad at king tom 
q what are the ramifications of this 
a hard to say but we hear that king toms producer just got a 
very big blowgun and now hes trying to find a heatseeking 
missile to put in it i dont know why 
q what is this doublepump thing of nbc 
