income floor for older women and that the real problem lies with 
their eligibility for private pensions 
many women receive no pensions because they tend to work in the 
service industry or for smaller firms that do not provide them 
hughes said that if an elderly couple is living on the husbands 
pension and he dies first the wife generally receives only a 
fraction in survivors benefits 
