<TEXT>
opec said monday it will not hold an 
emergency session to consider increasing oil production to help 
make up for the shortage caused by the mideast crisis 
but analysts predicted saudi arabia the worlds largest oil 
exporter would fulfill its pledge to boost output by as much as 2 
